37 mobility compact commission:
38 (A) The commission is a joint interstate governmental
39 agency comprised of states that have enacted the interstate
40 teacher mobility compact.
41 (B) Nothing in this interstate compact shall be construed to
42 be a waiver of sovereign immunity.
