32 effectuate the compact's purposes and intent. The
33 provisions of this compact shall have standing as statutory
34 law.
35 (B) Venue is proper and judicial proceedings by or against
36 the commission shall be brought solely and exclusively in
37 a court of competent jurisdiction where the principal office
