10 (A) reside within the attendance area of the school
11 corporation; who
12 (B) are currently included in the ADM of the charter school;
13 and
14 (C) receive not more than fifty percent (50%) virtual
15 instruction.
16 STEP TWO: Determine the sum of:
17 (A) the current ADM count for the school corporation; plus
18 (B) the total number of students who:
19 (i) reside within the attendance area of the school
20 corporation; who:
