22 excluding virtual charter schools or adult high schools; and
23 (iii) do not receive more than fifty percent (50%) virtual
24 instruction.
25 STEP THREE: Determine the result of:
26 (A) the STEP ONE amount; divided by
27 (B) the STEP TWO amount.
28 STEP FOUR: Determine the result of:
29 (A) the STEP THREE amount; multiplied by
30 (B) the amount collected by the county auditor during the most
31 recent installment period.
